Slackware Current Repository by Conraid

======================================================================

davtest (WebDAV penetration testing tool)

This tool tests WebDAV servers for vulnerabilities by:
- Testing directory creation (MKCOL)
- Uploading files in various languages (PUT)
- Testing MOVE/COPY methods to bypass execution filters
- Verifying if uploaded files can be executed on the server
- Optionally uploading backdoors/shells to vulnerable targets

HOME: https://github.com/cldrn/davtest

======================================================================
REQUIRES: perl-crypt-ssleay perl-http-dav perl-xml-dom 

